[Description]
Patches in this directory is used to handle the different between the emulator and the STB.

[Usage]
Type command git apply [patch name].
For exmaple: git apply 0001-patch-for-box.patch

[0001-patch-for-box.patch]
This is the only neccessary one to keep the current code run on the STB. Contains some transparant function and handle errors which will crash the STB.

[0001-box_performance_log.patch]
This is used to check the CPU consumption of the main game scene. It will log the time & memory info to files, which can be view by cat /usr/squirrel/logfile.
